Package: HoopsImpact
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Evaluating Basketball Player Performance and Team Impact
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Robbie",
           family = "Hunter",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "hunter123@usf.edu",
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0000-0000-0000"))
Description: Provides a set of accessible functions for sports analytics work
    in basketball, including efficiency-based impact scoring, role
    classification of players, head-to-head player comparison, and
    visualization of player performance. The package is intended for
    students, analysts, and coaches who want to evaluate player
    contributions without building models from scratch. It bundles a
    sample dataset of player season statistics so that all functions can
    be demonstrated and tested out of the box.
